    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/80 mb-12 max-w-2xl font-medium animate-fade-in leading-relaxed drop-shadow-md" style="animation-delay: 0.3s;">
      Tell us your mood, budget, and time. Our AI instantly crafts the perfect personalized activity so you can get off the couch and do something amazing.
    </p>

    <!-- Clean CTA Button -->
